#circuitbreakersg day 38

One-pan roasted chicken thighs with assorted vegetable of egg plant, celery and mushrooms for dinner tonight. 🍗 🍆🌱
.
.
.
Pan seared the chicken thighs on the cast iron skillet to give the chicken skin a nice sear, did a quick stir fry of the vegetable in the same skillet, and then transferred the skillet into the oven for about 20 mins, and dinner is ready! ✌🏼
.
.
.
A quick and delicious dinner and I managed to clear some of the leftover vegetable in the fridge. 😃
.
.
.
I ordered coffee for the first time since circuit breaker started because I somehow felt a bit silly ordering coffee when I could just have coffee at home. But I decided to just indulge a little today and it was nice. ☕️ #gratitudediary
.
.
.
